Packages 
Package Description
xyz.swatt.asserts
Contains custom Assertions.
xyz.swatt.data_mapping_validator
This package contains helper classes for validating data being mapped from one location and/or format to another, typically through a process like a workflow.
xyz.swatt.exceptions
This package will contain all of the custom SWATT Exceptions.
xyz.swatt.files
This package contains classes for working with files and folders/directories.
xyz.swatt.json
This package contains tools for working with JSON data.
xyz.swatt.log
This package holds helper class to make logging easier.
xyz.swatt.pojo
This package contains Plain Old Java Object (POJO) helper classes and interfaces.
xyz.swatt.selenium
SWATT's Selenium package will help with testing Web Apps.
xyz.swatt.soap
SWATT's Soap package will help easily send Soap Requests and process the response.
xyz.swatt.string
Contains a Helper class to preform common and/or complex String manipulations.
xyz.swatt.testng.reporters
Custom Reporters to be used with TestNG Tests.
xyz.swatt.xml
This packages has classes to help with the parsing, writing, querying, and modifying of XML Documents.
